The image is a close-up shot of a beautiful pink and white Amaryllis flower. The caption mentions it's a "Nymph Amaryllis" intended to brighten a cold winter's day.
The image is a photograph of a beautiful sunset with orange and gray clouds. There are silhouetted trees at the bottom of the frame.

The image is a landscape photograph of a sunset over a lake or large body of water. There's a field in the foreground with a few people standing or walking on it. The sky is filled with vibrant orange and yellow hues.
